quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,82,"Jaabawol makko Й“en wonaano si wanaa ko Й“e wi'i : \"Yaltinee Й“e ka hoЙ—o mon ; kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e laЙ“Й“intintooЙ“e"
  7,83,"Men daЙ—ndi mo kanko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, si wanaa debbo makko on ; onЙ—on heddoduno e (leptaaЙ“e) Й“en"
  7,84,Men saaЖҙini toЙ“o e maЙ“Й“e. Ndaarii ko honno battane bomЙ“e Й“en laatornoo
  7,85,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e Madyana, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Su'aybu, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla. ReweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. GomЙ—ii Й“anngannduyee arii on immorde ka Joomi mon. Timminee etirЙ—e Й—en e manndikke Й—en, wata on Й—uytan yimЙ“e Й“en piiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, wata on bonnu ko leydi Й“aawo moЖҙЖҙugol ndi. Ko Й—um mooЙ—on Й“uri on moЖҙЖҙannde si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  7,86,"Wata on jooЙ—o e kala laawol, hiЙ—on kammba, hiЙ—on sakko=faloo e laawol Alla ngol Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Mo, hiЙ—on Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұaare. Annditee tuma nde wonnoЙ—on seeЙ—aaЙ“e O Й—uЙ—Й—ini on. Ndaaree honno battane bonnooЙ“e Й“en laatornoo"
  7,87,"Si wonii fedde e mooЙ—on gomЙ—inii kon ko Nuliraa e mun, fedde goo gomЙ—inaali, muГұГұee haa Alla Гұaawa hakkunde me'en. Ko Kanko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“en"
